  m_text: 'Focus: Explaining the UI elements like your progress bar.


    Tracking
    Player Success:


    a. Progress Bar: The progress panel in your screen show
    which "Scene" of the rescue  chain you are in.


    b. Scene Completion: Once
    all tasks are completed, select "Next Step" from the control UI panel.


    c.
    Emergency Call: In Scene 4, you must report the specific injuries you observedon
    vicitm and share accident location  to the operator.'
