  m_text: 'Focus: Reducing motion sickness and teaching VR navigation.


    How
    to Move:


    a. Left Thumbstick: Move your character forward, backward, left,
    and right.


    b. Right Thumbstick: "Snap Turn" to rotate your view without
    getting dizzy.


    c. Physical Movement: You can teleport within scenes. Just
    point to the location and use the controller grab.


    d. Scene Center: If
    your game scene not in the view, press meta quest button on the controller. It
    resets the view.'
